repository.name: master-containerized-microservices
repository.description: This repo contains a sample application based on a fictional eCommerce. The primary goal of this sample is to demonstrate several software-architecture concepts like: Clean Architecture, Microservices, CQRS, Event Sourcing, Publish-Subscribe Architecture, Domain Driven Design (DDD). Currently this is a work in progress.
